abstract: Chez Reavie leads opening round of AT&T Pebble Beach Pro-Am golf tournament in California; other golf news noted.

headline.main: Chez Reavie Leads at Pebble Beach

snippet: Chez Reavie opened with an eight-under-par 63 at Monterey Peninsula to take the lead Thursday after one round of the AT&T Pebble Beach Pro-Am in California.
lead_paragraph: Chez Reavie opened with an eight-under-par 63 at Monterey Peninsula to take the lead Thursday after one round of the AT&T Pebble Beach Pro-Am in California.
